query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 0
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('android-adapter',
'asp.net-core-2.0',
'average',
'docusignapi',
'export-to-excel',
'facebook-like',
'hashtable',
'joomla3.0',
'packages',
'scrollbar',
'uigesturerecognizer');
